<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
P0741: Torque Converter Clutch Circuit Performance / Stuck Off
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Slip revolution for torque converter, which is calculated from primary pulley speed and engine speed, is more than specified value even if TCC solenoid valve is ON.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(2 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
TCC solenoid valve (CVT assembly) and/or its circuit
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Torque converter
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
TCM
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</servinfosub>
